title: Reg Organizer 8.20 Final RePack
description:
A multifunctional program for editing, cleaning and maintaining the registry, fixing errors in the system and improving its performance. The deep registry search will allow you to find all the registry keys related to the application you are interested in. The program allows you to edit the registry (. Reg) files and view their contents directly from Windows Explorer. Contains the uninstaller of applications, allowing to completely remove unnecessary programs from the system. A number of other functions will be useful to both administrators and ordinary users.
ATTENTION!!!
To prevent the "rally" registration, add the file UpdaterDll.dll (located in the folder with the program),
in the exception of antivirus.
Also, it is possible to FALSE detect antivirus on repack on the complaint of the legal owner
